<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Maximous Smacklayer</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-06 00:46:16</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>heres the quest,  you have to find Lynuga a Female troll NPC wandering around in innothule swamp, you talk to her about her gem collection, and she talks about a ruby, there is a gem merchant in Grobb, assuming that you can go in grobb, that you can buy rubies off of, he is located in a maze like place on the left of the shaman guild. when you give Lynuga a ruby (assuming you find her) she says oh you found my gem collection, or soemthing along those lines, and gives you one of these three items :  Brutechopper 16/50 2hslash trl/ogr/de only i believe, Midnight mallet 14/44 5or 10 charges of walking sleep clr shm  trl ogr bar dwf only, Ivandyr's Hoop 6wis, 6int, 6ac, 6hp, 6charges of spirit tap (very very rare), and the way you get lynuga to spawn is you have to kill zimbittle, a roaming low lvl troll npc, very annoying i might add, and i believe that makes lynuga spawn.  Im not totally certain but i believe you ahve to have one brutechopper, and one mallet then you can have a chance at the earring, not totally certain though, i hope this helps some of you if you were confused about the quest. as far as i know there is no way to raise faction with trolls, including lynuga.</font></td></tr></table>
